Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Time difference between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' before 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes for a case to be resubmitted after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Time difference between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in resubmitted cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases leading to process iteration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases with multiple rejections before final approval
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR occurs
